A Studio Ghibli style illustration of a fierce but gentle dragon mother curled protectively around two small dragon hatchlings in a cozy forest den, her scales shimmering with iridescent greens and golds, soft dappled sunlight filtering through ancient trees above, wildflowers blooming around the entrance, the mother dragon's expression warm yet with a subtle warning glint in her amber eyes, the baby dragons playfully tumbling over each other, magical fireflies floating in the air, warm earthy tones with touches of magical luminescence throughout the scene.
